headline: IQVIA CFO Ron Bruehlman to Speak at the TD Cowen Annual Health Care Conference on March 4, 2025
summary: RESEARCH TRIANGLE PARK, N.C., February 21, 2025--IQVIA Holdings Inc. ("IQVIA") (NYSE:IQV) announced today that Ron Bruehlman, executive vice president and chief financial officer, will speak at the TD Cowen Annual Health Care Conference on Tuesday, March 4, 2025, at 11:10 a.m. ET.
